 #404040; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Before t=
hat, during his teenage years in the 1930s, Vonnegut saw Franklin D. Roosev=
elt&#8217;s Works Progress Administration use federal funds to employ milli=
ons of unemployed Americans in public works projects to help overcome a tem=
porary Great Depression.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: #404040; font-size: 16=
px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><em>Player Piano </em><span>ask=
ed, &#8220;What if the GE engineers get their way?&#8221; and answered with=
