an>:</span></p><blockquote style=3D"border-left: 4px solid #67bdfc; margin:=
 20px 0; padding: 0;"><p style=3D"color: #404040; font-size: 16px; line-hei=
ght: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0; margin-left: 20px;"><em><span>Player Piano w=
as my response to the implications of having everything run by little boxes=
=2E The idea of doing that, you know, mad=
e sense, perfect sense. To have a li=
ttle clicking box make all the decisions wasn't a vicious thing to do. </sp=
an><strong>But it was too bad for the human beings who got their dignity fr=
