episode was titled &#8220;The Forever Games,&#8221; and near the very begin=
ning, Lasky laid out the five key attributes of Forever Games, &#8220;games=
 designed to last for a really long time.&#8221;&#160;</span></p><ol style=
=3D"margin-top: 0; padding: 0;"><li style=3D"margin: 8px 0 0 32px;"><p styl=
e=3D"box-sizing: border-box; color: #404040; font-size: 16px; line-height: =
26px; margin: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-left: 4px;"><strong>Balance: </s=
