6px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Not every Forever Game needs t=
o be 100% on every category, but they need to have at least a little of eac=
h, and ideally a lot of some.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: #404040; font-siz=
e: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">That framework fits a lot =
of the jobs that have become more popular since the 1800s, and especially o=
