 obvious ones fit, too. Academia, product management, certainly newsletter =
writing. Think about your job: would you say it&#8217;s more &#8220;life or=
 death&#8221; or &#8220;game-like&#8221;? When I asked that question on Twi=
tter, 81% of respondents went with game-like:</p><div class=3D"tweet static=
